flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 31: Closed-Loop Forecast Feedback and Retraining Trigger Flow

  WeeklyCron[Weekly CRON\nSunday midnight]
  LoadData[Load ai_forecasts + actual sales]
  ErrorCalc[Compute forecast_error\nabsolute difference between predicted and actual divided by actual]
  PersistAccuracy[(Write forecast_accuracy table)]

  ProductFlag{rolling_avg_error > 0.25\nfor product?}
  MarkProduct[Mark product for retrain]
  KeepProduct[No retrain flag for product]
  PersistFlags[(Persist product retrain flags)]

  FleetCheck{Flagged products > 30%?}
  TriggerRetrain[Trigger full model retrain job]
  RetrainResult{Retrain successful?}

  DeployModel[Deploy new model_version\nfor future inference]
  KeepCurrent[Keep prior model_version active]
  Incident[(Log retrain incident + audit trail\nfor follow-up)]

  ContinueLoop[Continue weekly feedback loop]

  WeeklyCron --> LoadData --> ErrorCalc --> PersistAccuracy --> ProductFlag
  ProductFlag -- Yes --> MarkProduct --> PersistFlags --> FleetCheck
  ProductFlag -- No --> KeepProduct --> FleetCheck

  FleetCheck -- Yes --> TriggerRetrain --> RetrainResult
  RetrainResult -- Yes --> DeployModel --> ContinueLoop
  RetrainResult -- No --> KeepCurrent --> Incident --> ContinueLoop

  FleetCheck -- No --> ContinueLoop
